The '''Cordel Cove Winter Carnival''' was an annual celebration that took place in [[Cordel Cove]], the largest settlement on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Neftali/Legends|Neftali]]. Centered on celebrating the beauty of the ice world, the carnival's events included [[Swoop racing/Legends|swoop races]] through ice caverns, ice sculptures, and beverages made with Neftalian pure-ice [[Water/Legends|water]]. The largest festival in the [[Socorro system/Legends|Socorro system]], the carnival drew in tourists from across the [[Sector/Legends|sector]].

